You will be asked to create a crowd marketplace (e.g., like Uber or Amazon Mechanical Turk) using our system. We will provide an example of a crowd marketplace idea to show you the structure that you will follow to describe your idea. After defining an idea, you will complete forms on our platform to start to create this marketplace. The forms will ask you to customize and create a crowd market following your crowd market idea. It is important to complete the forms carefully, especially think about how your selected options could affect the overall design of the crowd market you will create. If an option in the forms is not present in your description, try to infer the answer based on what you are trying to create.

Crowd Market Example: This is a crowd market that focuses on delivering rides through an app. The crowd market connects people who need a ride (passengers) with people who can offer a ride (drivers). This crowd market offers two main services: X, that are rides from drivers who drive a non-luxury vehicle and Black that are provided from drivers who drive luxury vehicles. The crowd market charges passengers a fee calculated by their platform once the service has ended. The Crowd market platform takes a percentage for every ride income and the rest goes to the driver. The service is available only in some cities and countries.

Now is your turn to describe an idea different than the example. As the example shows you will describe how your crowd marketplace connects "Who offers" with "Who needs" and how this enables people to collaborate. The idea should describe what is offered and how it’s accomplished by both sides. Try to cover at least the points covered by the example. Some other examples of crowd markets are: Platforms that connect patients with doctors, Pet walkers with pet owners, buyers with sellers, people who have an extra room with travelers, restaurants who have excess of food with assistance centers, etc. Think about what is needed in your region and describe it in the same format as the example.

<script>
var userId = uuidv4();

jQuery(function(){
  jQuery('body').on('DOMNodeInserted', '.fillable', function(e) {
    if (e.target.tagName != "LABEL") {
      gigConnectFields(this);
    }
  });
  jQuery(".fillable").each(function(){
    gigConnectFields(this);
  });
  jQuery(".trackable").focusin(function(){
    ga('send', {
      hitType: 'event',
      eventCategory: userId,
      eventAction: jQuery(this).attr('id'),
      eventLabel: 'focusin'
    });
  });
  jQuery(".trackable").focusout(function(){
    ga('send', {
      hitType: 'event',
      eventCategory: userId,
      eventAction: jQuery(this).attr('id'),
      eventLabel: 'focusout'
    });
  });
  jQuery(".next_6").click(function(){
    jQuery(".borderColors").find("input").val(userId);
  });
});

function gigConnectFields(source) {
  var inputs = jQuery(source).find("input");
  if (inputs.length > 0) {
    inputs.each(function(){
      var option = this;
      var parentElement = jQuery(this).parent().parent();
      var fieldValue = jQuery(option).val();
      var matches = fieldValue.match(/{local:(.*?)}/);
      if (matches.length > 1) {
        var field = matches.pop();
        var fieldQuery = "." + field + " input";
        var fieldObject = jQuery(fieldQuery);
        var fieldValue = "";
        if (fieldObject.length > 0) {
          fieldValue = fieldObject.val();
          jQuery(option).val(fieldValue);
          jQuery("label[for='" + option.id + "']").contents().last().replaceWith(" " + fieldValue);
        }
        if (fieldValue == "") {
          parentElement.hide();
        } else {
          parentElement.show();
        }
        jQuery(document).on("input", fieldQuery, function() {
          var fieldObject = jQuery(fieldQuery);
          var fieldValue = fieldObject.val();
          jQuery(option).val(fieldValue);
          jQuery("label[for='" + option.id + "']").contents().last().replaceWith(" " + fieldValue);
          if (fieldValue == "") {
            parentElement.hide();
          } else {
            parentElement.show();
          }
        });
      }
    });  
  }
}

function uuidv4() {
  return 'xxxxxxxx-xxxx-4xxx-yxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx'.replace(/[xy]/g, function(c) {
    var r = Math.random() * 16 | 0, v = c == 'x' ? r : (r & 0x3 | 0x8);
    return v.toString(16);
  });
}
</script>
